ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999997251507, \"rank\": 2.7485575137003757e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Rabadan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre Rabadan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Rabadan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_Rabadan\"}, {\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999997251507, \"rank\": 2.7485575137003757e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic logo in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999997251507, \"rank\": 2.7485575137003757e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9965423386451119, \"rank\": 0.0017677901874359654, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  \\\"We have the possibility to reduce the impact and the facilities of the opening ceremony if the international risk becomes harder,\\\" Rabadan said.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rabadan\", \"score\": 0.9999999991212007, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rabadan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rabadan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rabadan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can reduce it, the show, the number of people.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is no plan B.\\\"\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, we talk about hypotheses,\\\" Gregoire added.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are focused on preparing the situation.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are doing our best to guarantee security with major, major measures.\\\"\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to The Athletic, as many as one million people, including residents who live near the Olympic Games sites, will be screened before July 26.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Athletic\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organizers revealed there will be controls on the movement of people into homes next to the Seine before and during the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999847416759414, \"rank\": 0.00012310608002513926, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The police need to check who they are in case they represent a threat to security,\\\" Gregoire said.\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They will have strong security measures days before.\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea is to maintain the possibility that neighbors can welcome friends and family.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time [we need to] to guarantee security.\\\"\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}]}"